# Brand DNA — Sofia Mosquera

## Colors (NEVER deviate)
- Background: `#F5F3EE` (blanco calido) — NEVER `#FFFFFF`
- Text: `#111111` (negro base) — NEVER `#000000`
- Body text: `#1A1A1A` (negro suave)
- Navigation/muted: `#B5B0A8` (gris nav)
- Card backgrounds: `#EAE7E0` (crema)
- Borders: `#D5D1CA` (gris border)

## Typography
- Headings: `font-heading` (Instrument Serif) — weight 400, NEVER bold
- Body: `font-body` (Jost) — weights 200, 300, 400
- Label/metadata: `font-body` with `text-[9px]-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] uppercase`

## Components
- Use `@sofi/ui` components (Button, WhatsAppCTA, SectionReveal, Marquee)
- Images: always `next/image` with `fill` + `sizes`, never raw `<img>`
- Motion: always check `prefers-reduced-motion`
- WhatsApp CTA: phone +5492615456913, use pre-crafted messages

## Vocabulary
- Use "interiorismo" not "decoración"
- Use "espacio" not "casa linda"
- Never use "barato", "económico", "oferta"
- CTA style: "Coordiná tu asesoría", "Consultá tu proyecto"
